73
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:06,330
[Wrong. A death at the construction site.]
[Hello. Can we talk?]

74
00:06:06,330 --> 00:06:07,210
Go find him.

75
00:06:07,550 --> 00:06:08,540
Ask him what happened

76
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:10,270
and why he posted this comment.

77
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,120
