if he doesn't tell the truth.

78
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,800
Wen Bo.

79
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:17,840
There's one more thing.

80
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,300
We found out who smeared us online

81
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:20,480
when we arrested Zheng Gao

82
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,210
previously.

83
00:06:23,030 --> 00:06:24,260
Liu Tianfei hired him.

84
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:25,860
The middleman was Xu Jiajun.

85
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,140
Uncle Tianfei?

86
00:06:35,590 --> 00:06:36,200
Got it.

87
00:06:39,690 --> 00:06:40,950
I'll follow up on that.

88
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,400
Continue.

89
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,180
Xin.

90
00:07:00,710 --> 00:07:01,540
Xin,

91
00:07:01,570 --> 00:07:02,370
there you are.

92
00:07:02,590 --> 00:07:04,120
I was just out for a meeting.

93
00:07:06,570 --> 00:07:07,680
Your assistant...

94
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,070
Named Meng Yu, right?

95
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:10,380
Why isn't she with you?

96
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:11,750
She has resigned.

97
00:07:13,710 --> 00:07:14,910
Shall we go for a ride?

98
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,830
Please let me take a rest.

99
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,310
I think you have a real talent
for horse riding.

100
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:22,310
You're even getting better than me.

101
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:23,690
That's not true.

102
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,880
It all thanks to you
for being a great tutor.

103
00:07:27,010 --> 00:07:29,510
Have you thought about
keeping your own horse?

104
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:30,970
I'm still just a beginner.

105
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:32,950
It's too soon to think about that.

106
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:34,750
Preparation is not necessarily a must

107
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:35,610
before action.

108
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,360
But now,

109
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,820
I have too much going on

110
00:07:40,620 --> 00:07:41,530
both at home

111
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:43,270
and in the company.

112
00:07:44,790 --> 00:07:46,680
There's very little time for myself.

113
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,920
How can I find time
to take care of a horse?

114
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,800
You can consult your brother
about company affairs.

115
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,000
He and you are family.

116
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,630
Why do everything on your own?

117
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,960
I hate to rely on others,

118
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:56,480
especially my brother.

119
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:58,320
Business and family

120
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,080
had better be separated.

121
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,530
You're just like your brother,

122
00:08:02,530 --> 00:08:04,190
so respectful of boundaries.

123
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,450
If the two of you joined forces,

124
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:09,530
there might not be a place
for me and Xinrui Group.

125
00:08:10,570 --> 00:08:11,770
You're joking again.

126
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,010
Xin,

127
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:16,630
how's the Hangang Center incident
being handled?

128
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,280
Everything's fine.

129
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,940
Hasn't your brother told you?

130
00:08:22,770 --> 00:08:24,770
No. Maybe he's too busy to inform me.

131
00:08:26,860 --> 00:08:28,260
Come on, have some fruit.

132
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,000
Thank you.

133
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,970
What do you think of this

134
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,400
newly arrived wine?

135
00:08:37,490 --> 00:08:38,169
It's okay.

136
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:39,450
It agrees well with me.

137
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:41,720
But I'm telling you,

138
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,120
everything works for me,

139
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,810
as long as it's alcohol.

140
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:48,290
It strikes me as a little light-bodied.

141
00:08:49,030 --> 00:08:50,090
Mediocre, I'd say.

142
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:51,800
I agree.

143
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,720
This wine is beneath us.

144
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,480
Anything wrong, Tianye?

145
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:00,650
Baoshuai!

146
00:09:06,900 --> 00:09:09,000
Mr. Wei forsook his construction business

147
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,250
for smuggling liquor

148
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,450
without telling me.

149
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:12,970
Mr. Liu,

150
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,400
I'm so sorry.

151
00:09:14,590 --> 00:09:15,940
I beg for a second chance,

152
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:16,540
Mr. Liu.

153
00:09:18,690 --> 00:09:19,420
I understand

154
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:22,040
that you're eager to make money.

155
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:24,000
But there are certain types of business

156
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,050
you can't touch.

157
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,440
Mr. Wei told me that it was you

158
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,440
who encouraged him to do smuggling,

159
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,730
and that you invested much money in it.

160
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,150
Is that true?

161
00:09:34,020 --> 00:09:34,540
Tianye,

162
00:09:35,070 --> 00:09:35,580
I...

163
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:37,840
Last month, you spent a fortune

164
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,780
on two watches.

165
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:41,350
Where did you hide them?

166
00:09:45,530 --> 00:09:46,190
They're...

167
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,310
in my apartment downtown.

168
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,850
I bought that apartment for Jiangyan.

169
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:53,470
Jiajun.

170
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:55,330
Jiangyan

171
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,510
is my only sister.

172
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:59,170
I can't just watch you lie to her

173
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:00,750
and do nothing.

174
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,080
Tianye,

175
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,530
we're all family here.

176
00:10:05,530 --> 00:10:07,060
Let's talk things through.

177
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:11,470
I'll take Mr. Wei out now.

178
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:14,350
Tianye...

179
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,160
Well, Tianye,

180
00:10:16,230 --> 00:10:17,630
I bet Jiajun knows he has done wrong.

181
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:19,360
Such seriousness is uncalled for.

182
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,340
I'm sorry, Tianye.

183
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:21,670
Tianye,

184
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,050
I admit

185
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,000
I'm in the wrong.

186
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,170
I was just

187
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,520
desperate to make money

188
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,720
and to build my own business.

189
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,030
That was why I foolishly...

190
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:31,840
Tianye, could you please keep it secret

191
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,700
from Jiangyan?

192
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:33,720
I promise

193
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,360
there won't be a next time.

194
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,090
"Next time"?

195
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:38,520
This is enough, Tianye.

196
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:39,920
We're all family here.

197
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:40,940
"Family"?

198
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:43,600
What kind of family
would do such stupid things?

199
00:10:43,690 --> 00:10:45,080
Did you two launch that smear campaign

200
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,680
when Zheng Gao was arrested?

201
00:10:48,660 --> 00:10:49,150
Tianye,

202
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:51,190
I'm sorry.

203
00:10:51,330 --> 00:10:51,720
I...

204
00:10:51,780 --> 00:10:52,910
Was I asking you?

205
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:55,750
If you dare hide anything

206
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:56,550
from me again,

207
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,680
you'll die a painful death.

208
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:00,590
Get lost.

209
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,250
Tianye,

210
00:11:15,420 --> 00:11:16,080
I'm to blame

211
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:17,280
for this matter.

212
00:11:17,730 --> 00:11:18,530
It's my fault.

213
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:20,610
I shouldn't have involved Jiajun.

214
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:21,480
However...

215
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:22,710
Tianye,

216
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:24,560
I think you're also well aware

217
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:27,060
that Feng has been coming after us
frantically for years...

218
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:28,050
Shut up.

219
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:30,800
What was it for when we took

220
00:11:31,590 --> 00:11:33,340
all that trouble to clean up the mess?

221
00:11:33,340 --> 00:11:35,470
We only did it to redirect the flak
to Zhang Xin.

222
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:37,000
Why did you pull that stunt?

223
00:11:37,950 --> 00:11:39,900
Wouldn't Qin Feng investigate it himself?

224
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:41,420
Uncle Tianye, actually...

225
00:11:41,420 --> 00:11:42,550
I'm partly to blame.

226
00:11:43,050 --> 00:11:44,670
If I hadn't lost the cufflinks

227
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:45,340
and...

228
00:11:47,230 --> 00:11:49,020
Alright, stop it, Baoshuai.

229
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:50,430
You stay out of this.

230
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:52,110
It has nothing to do with you.

231
00:11:52,470 --> 00:11:53,400
This is my fault,

232
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:54,630
entirely.

233
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:55,700
Tianye,

234
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:57,750
I've already owned up to it,

235
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:58,410
alright?

236
00:11:58,750 --> 00:11:59,880
To be honest,

237
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:01,100
Feng has been after us

238
00:12:01,110 --> 00:12:02,940
over these many years.

239
00:12:03,060 --> 00:12:03,540
Right?

240
00:12:03,650 --> 00:12:04,220
Tell me.

241
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,060
What else could I have done?

242
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:05,820
We're family.

243
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:07,420
Would I have possibly hurt him?

244
00:12:07,420 --> 00:12:09,060
But there had to be
an answer to his actions,

245
00:12:09,060 --> 00:12:10,020
or a solution, right?

246
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:11,350
That can't justify what you did!

247
00:12:11,350 --> 00:12:13,550
Then what do you think I should've done?

248
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:15,630
Does Feng even take us as his family?

249
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:17,270
He's now trying to tear

250
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:18,450
the family apart.

251
00:12:18,540 --> 00:12:19,820
Don't you understand?

252
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:22,870
-Why don't you let me speak?
-Stop running your mouth.

253
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:26,700
Go on.

254
00:12:27,690 --> 00:12:28,550
I'm listening.

255
00:12:36,650 --> 00:12:39,550
Tucked right into my pocket.
Tucked right into my pocket.

256
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:40,510
Back then, how do you think Ma Jin

257
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:42,380
and Luo Bo figured out we took the money?

258
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:45,980
Would Jiangyong have died
if you had kept your hands to yourself?

259
00:12:48,610 --> 00:12:49,740
Look what has become

260
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,410
of you in recent years.

261
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:55,120
A complete mess
living in a drunken stupor.

262
00:12:57,410 --> 00:12:59,680
I know you're upset
about Jiangyong's death.

263
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:00,620
I'm not blaming you.

264
00:13:00,620 --> 00:13:02,680
We're all responsible for his death.

265
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:04,460
But Tianfei,

266
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:07,400
you can't go on in this way.

267
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:09,960
The family needs you.

268
00:13:17,690 --> 00:13:18,220
Alright.

269
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:19,370
Enough.

270
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:20,710
Stop it, Tianfei.

271
00:13:20,750 --> 00:13:21,390
Stop it!

272
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:26,070
It's time you quit drinking.

273
00:13:26,470 --> 00:13:27,090
Tianye.

274
00:13:28,230 --> 00:13:28,890
Tianye!

275
00:13:49,470 --> 00:13:50,980
So far, Liu Tianye has only found out

276
00:13:50,980 --> 00:13:52,710
the business I did with Mr. Wei.

277
00:13:53,490 --> 00:13:54,690
He doesn't know about

278
00:13:54,860 --> 00:13:55,860
our dealings yet.

279
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:57,580
He got so mad

280
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,030
over such a minor issue.

281
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:01,960
They still haven't accepted you.

282
00:14:03,990 --> 00:14:07,050
Those from Longwan
are just a bunch of country bumpkins

283
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:09,070
who only trust their relatives.

284
00:14:09,070 --> 00:14:10,740
They're no different
than those heinous landlords

285
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:11,870
from centuries ago.

286
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,040
Ms. Zhang.

287
00:14:15,790 --> 00:14:17,700
I'm fed up with staying in Longwan.

288
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:18,900
I want to work for you.

289
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:21,410
You're one of Longwan people now.

290
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:23,540
If they know you've turned to me,

291
00:14:23,860 --> 00:14:26,260
your life will become even more difficult.

292
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:29,290
One of Longwan people?

293
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:33,550
Has any of them ever treated me
as one of Longwan people?

294
00:14:33,550 --> 00:14:34,820
They all look down on me,

295
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:37,500
calling me an outsider
who sponges off his wife.

296
00:14:37,860 --> 00:14:41,190
Every day, I'm like walking on eggshells
around Liu Tianye.

297
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:44,000
I'm so sick of this pathetic life.

298
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:46,670
I'll divorce his sister if I have to.

299
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:47,400
You must not.

300
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:50,960
Why not?

301
00:14:51,620 --> 00:14:52,950
Once you leave Longwan,

302
00:14:52,980 --> 00:14:54,040
you'll be of no use.

303
00:14:58,460 --> 00:14:59,390
What do you mean?

304
00:15:02,580 --> 00:15:04,040
Just stay in Longwan.

305
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:05,050
Perhaps

306
00:15:05,430 --> 00:15:07,080
I'll need you for something.

307
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:13,670
All of you are using me as a tool,

308
00:15:13,700 --> 00:15:14,220
right?

309
00:15:14,650 --> 00:15:16,270
Am I a slave to you guys?

310
00:15:16,820 --> 00:15:17,470
Ms. Zhang,

311
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:20,550
haven't I done much work for you
over these years?

312
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:22,550
You think you've worked for me?

313
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:25,500
I just helped you make some money.

314
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:27,230
Have you forgotten who you are?

315
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:28,670
Right.

316
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:30,900
Your business

317
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:32,530
is way out of my league.

318
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:34,320
I'll quit then, okay?

319
00:15:34,670 --> 00:15:36,220
Do you think you'll get to live

320
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:39,460
if Liu Tianye finds out about
the dirty stuff you've been using

321
00:15:39,460 --> 00:15:40,920
Longwan's companies for?

322
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:46,500
Just the money you've laundered already
amounts to dozens of millions, right?

323
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:48,040
If word gets out,

324
00:15:49,270 --> 00:15:51,730
your wife and child
will both be implicated.

325
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:56,970
I get it.

326
00:15:58,980 --> 00:16:01,580
You plan to threaten Liu Tianye
with Jiangyan.

327
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:05,020
What a deliberate scheme of yours.

328
00:16:06,390 --> 00:16:07,750
It turns out
you've been having this evil plan

329
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:10,550
in mind
while pretending to be Jiangyan's friend.

330
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:12,960
Given the line of business I'm in,

331
00:16:13,430 --> 00:16:15,160
I have to leave myself a way out.

332
00:16:15,910 --> 00:16:16,790
I've heard

333
00:16:16,950 --> 00:16:18,470
that you're being ousted

334
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:20,620
from the Hangzhou Port project.

335
00:16:24,670 --> 00:16:25,520
Xu Jiajun,

336
00:16:26,430 --> 00:16:29,030
just go back to Longwan
and mooch off your wife.

337
00:16:29,430 --> 00:16:30,630
You'd better behave,

338
00:16:31,190 --> 00:16:32,850
or I'll have your whole family

339
00:16:33,220 --> 00:16:35,620
suffer for what you've done
in these years.

340
00:16:52,700 --> 00:16:53,310
Xu Jiajun!

341
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:57,350
What's wrong, honey?

342
00:16:57,500 --> 00:16:58,720
What is this about?

343
00:16:58,900 --> 00:16:59,310
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau
enforced the law violently]

344
00:16:59,310 --> 00:17:01,190
Why would this college mate of yours

345
00:17:01,190 --> 00:17:02,810
write such an article to criticize

346
00:17:02,810 --> 00:17:04,609
my brother and the police force?

347
00:17:04,910 --> 00:17:06,040
I asked him about it.

348
00:17:06,089 --> 00:17:07,890
He said he was introduced by you!

349
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:10,670
Honey,

350
00:17:10,670 --> 00:17:12,390
-sit down and hear me out.
-Don't touch me!

351
00:17:12,390 --> 00:17:13,050
Explain it!

352
00:17:13,910 --> 00:17:14,790
Oh, please,

353
00:17:14,910 --> 00:17:15,920
just hear me out.

354
00:17:15,950 --> 00:17:17,410
It's a misunderstanding.

355
00:17:17,540 --> 00:17:19,220
I was deceived by Tianfei.

356
00:17:19,300 --> 00:17:20,869
He asked me to introduce
someone from the press

357
00:17:20,869 --> 00:17:22,349
to him, claiming that he was doing

358
00:17:22,349 --> 00:17:23,579
another person a favor.

359
00:17:23,579 --> 00:17:25,380
I didn't ask for more specifics.

360
00:17:26,260 --> 00:17:27,630
Look what a mess it has become.

361
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:29,390
It's my fault for being too thoughtless.

362
00:17:29,390 --> 00:17:31,700
Who would've known he'd do such a thing?

363
00:17:31,910 --> 00:17:32,900
If I had realized it,

364
00:17:32,900 --> 00:17:34,570
I wouldn't have introduced anyone to him.

365
00:17:34,570 --> 00:17:35,770
Why didn't you tell me

366
00:17:36,330 --> 00:17:37,730
the whole story earlier?

367
00:17:38,050 --> 00:17:40,370
I just felt too awkward about this

368
00:17:40,370 --> 00:17:41,530
and didn't know how to tell you about it.

369
00:17:41,530 --> 00:17:42,190
But mainly,

370
00:17:42,330 --> 00:17:43,370
I didn't want to worry you.

371
00:17:43,370 --> 00:17:44,440
Drop the act!

372
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:47,350
How much did Liu Tianfei pay you?

373
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:48,980
Zero, honey.

374
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:50,620
How could I have taken money?

375
00:17:50,850 --> 00:17:52,700
Honey, I admit I did wrong.

376
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:53,740
I'm sorry.

377
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:56,040
I should've been more careful.

378
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:56,980
My apologies.

379
00:17:57,020 --> 00:17:58,950
I promise this won't happen again.

380
00:18:00,130 --> 00:18:01,340
I'm warning you,

381
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:03,530
cut off contact with Liu Tianfei

382
00:18:03,530 --> 00:18:04,740
from now on.

383
00:18:05,530 --> 00:18:06,900
Longwan and Tianyun

384
00:18:07,260 --> 00:18:08,460
are not associated in any way!

385
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:09,720
Yes, sure, honey.

386
00:18:10,090 --> 00:18:11,010
I'm sorry.

387
00:18:11,090 --> 00:18:11,740
I know

388
00:18:11,900 --> 00:18:12,890
I did wrong.

389
00:18:15,370 --> 00:18:15,850
Tianye.

390
00:18:17,290 --> 00:18:19,090
Why didn't you tell me about your visit?

391
00:18:19,090 --> 00:18:22,150
Tianfei had someone write an article
attacking Crazy.

392
00:18:22,330 --> 00:18:23,260
Do you know that?

393
00:18:24,050 --> 00:18:24,570
Yes.

394
00:18:24,950 --> 00:18:26,280
Did you tell him to do so?

395
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:26,850
No.

396
00:18:29,110 --> 00:18:30,640
You heard that from Jiajun?

397
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:32,170
Yes.

398
00:18:35,870 --> 00:18:36,760
Now,

399
00:18:37,010 --> 00:18:38,090
Tianyun is about to be a contractor

400
00:18:38,090 --> 00:18:39,820
of the Hangang Center project.

401
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:41,540
This is a crucial time for us.

402
00:18:41,950 --> 00:18:43,950
So I wouldn't let my people go rogue.

403
00:18:44,150 --> 00:18:46,050
But in this matter, Tianfei and his guys

404
00:18:46,050 --> 00:18:46,990
have really gone out of line.

405
00:18:46,990 --> 00:18:48,290
I've reprimanded them.

406
00:18:48,290 --> 00:18:49,750
Then keep Tianfei in line.

407
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:53,340
I'd hate to see anything like that
happen again.

408
00:18:53,660 --> 00:18:54,180
Got it.

409
00:18:57,220 --> 00:18:57,810
Sit down.

410
00:18:58,500 --> 00:18:59,420
Why so mad?

411
00:18:59,420 --> 00:18:59,850
Sit.

412
00:19:07,850 --> 00:19:08,420
How is

413
00:19:09,290 --> 00:19:10,690
Jiajun treating you now?

414
00:19:13,850 --> 00:19:15,380
Why ask that out of a sudden?

415
00:19:17,980 --> 00:19:20,380
I think you should spend more time
managing

416
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:21,700
the company affairs.

417
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:23,940
Sometimes Jiajun could be too impulsive.

418
00:19:23,940 --> 00:19:25,540
I'm worried that he might...

419
00:19:26,090 --> 00:19:26,750
get conned.

420
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:29,950
What exactly are you trying to say?

421
00:19:31,420 --> 00:19:31,740
All I want

422
00:19:31,740 --> 00:19:33,470
is for you to live a better life.

423
00:19:34,220 --> 00:19:36,280
Tianyun is operating quite well now.

424
00:19:36,900 --> 00:19:37,610
Actually,

425
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:39,500
it's fine for you to step down

426
00:19:39,770 --> 00:19:40,900
and enjoy your life.

427
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:42,740
We'll help if anything happens.

428
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:44,400
I've never asked for much.

429
00:19:47,180 --> 00:19:49,840
I just hope all of our family
to be safe and sound.

430
00:19:51,370 --> 00:19:51,940
Sure.

431
00:19:53,020 --> 00:19:55,420
What happened to Crazy won't happen again.

432
00:19:55,600 --> 00:19:56,210
I promise.

433
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:56,910
Alright?

434
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:28,980
Do me a favor.

435
00:20:30,220 --> 00:20:32,750
I think
my husband is keeping a secret from me.

436
00:20:33,570 --> 00:20:34,970
Find out what it is for me.

437
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:40,750
Captain Qin.

438
00:20:41,460 --> 00:20:42,460
I've got in contact

439
00:20:42,460 --> 00:20:44,050
with who posted that comment online.

440
00:20:44,050 --> 00:20:45,310
His name is Feng Jiang.

441
00:20:45,740 --> 00:20:46,740
He said his brother Feng Hai

442
00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:48,520
died in the Hangang Center incident.

443
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:49,420
Where is he now?

444
00:20:50,260 --> 00:20:51,390
He's very cautious,

445
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,720
and can only be contacted via internet.

446
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:56,790
Bian Jing.

447
00:20:57,770 --> 00:20:59,460
Check if there's anyone named Feng Hai

448
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:00,860
listed in the personnel involved.

449
00:21:00,860 --> 00:21:01,330
Okay.

450
00:21:11,460 --> 00:21:12,500
He's not on the list.

451
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:13,260
He's not?

452
00:21:15,820 --> 00:21:17,270
Keep in touch with Feng Jiang.

453
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:18,130
Ask him for details.

454
00:21:18,130 --> 00:21:19,660
If necessary, bring him in.

455
00:21:20,460 --> 00:21:20,860
Got it.

456
00:21:24,420 --> 00:21:24,820
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau]

457
00:21:24,820 --> 00:21:26,510
Any other person surnamed Feng?

458
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:27,210
I checked.

459
00:21:27,430 --> 00:21:28,290
There are none.

460
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:41,570
Crazy.

461
00:21:42,050 --> 00:21:43,010
I need a favor.

462
00:21:43,820 --> 00:21:44,910
Please contact

463
00:21:44,930 --> 00:21:46,560
the construction team

464
00:21:46,930 --> 00:21:49,990
of the Han Port project
and ask if someone named Feng Hai

465
00:21:50,150 --> 00:21:51,150
worked there.

466
00:21:52,950 --> 00:21:54,770
His brother, Feng Jiang, claimed

467
00:21:54,770 --> 00:21:56,600
that he died in the incident.

468
00:21:57,530 --> 00:21:58,510
Just make an inquiry.

469
00:21:58,510 --> 00:21:59,670
Okay. I'm on it.

470
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:18,700
Mai.

471
00:22:19,230 --> 00:22:20,950
I got Feng Jiang's address.

472
00:22:21,110 --> 00:22:23,700
A construction worker
said he knew Feng Jiang and his brother.

473
00:22:23,700 --> 00:22:25,160
Look, here's the address.

474
00:22:25,260 --> 00:22:27,000
[203 Taisheng Middle Road,
Xiling District, Hanzhou City]

475
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,540
[Unit 104, Building 3, Zizhu Compound]

476
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:35,480
[Hiring]

477
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:39,160
[Access cash from your credit line]

478
00:23:08,280 --> 00:23:09,090
[Panda Party]

479
00:23:09,090 --> 00:23:10,020
Their apartment

480
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:12,360
seems to have been vacant for some time.

481
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:16,230
They must be in hiding.

482
00:23:17,570 --> 00:23:19,830
Someone else is looking for them, right?

483
00:23:21,800 --> 00:23:23,680
Why is that car following us?

484
00:23:24,790 --> 00:23:25,560
Which car?

485
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,000
The one behind us.

486
00:23:32,470 --> 00:23:33,740
Isn't it your fault?

487
00:23:34,390 --> 00:23:35,520
For being caught up?

488
00:23:38,190 --> 00:23:41,120
Fine. Then hold on tight.
I'll show you what I've got.

489
00:23:43,530 --> 00:23:46,670
[Panda Party]

490
00:24:01,020 --> 00:24:02,850
Sir, back up a bit!

491
00:24:44,290 --> 00:24:44,910
Director Chu,

492
00:24:44,910 --> 00:24:46,500
not knowing what information they got,

493
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:47,740
I followed them all the way.

494
00:24:47,740 --> 00:24:49,070
But they were very alert

495
00:24:49,390 --> 00:24:50,480
and got rid of me.

496
00:24:51,840 --> 00:24:52,570
I heard you.

497
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:54,360
I'll have others follow them.

498
00:24:56,210 --> 00:24:57,150
Nobody move!

499
00:24:57,260 --> 00:24:58,520
-Squat down!
-Freeze!

500
00:24:58,570 --> 00:24:59,310
Don't move!

501
00:24:59,610 --> 00:25:00,640
What are you doing?

502
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,300
Who are you?

503
00:25:02,550 --> 00:25:03,350
Director Chu.

504
00:25:05,610 --> 00:25:06,410
Director Chu?

505
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:07,850
Director Chu.

506
00:25:09,020 --> 00:25:09,700
Well...

507
00:25:09,980 --> 00:25:11,580
Your skills have gone rusty.

508
00:25:11,770 --> 00:25:13,810
Get some practice after this is done.

509
00:25:13,810 --> 00:25:16,420
Sorry, Director Chu.
I'll do a better job next time.

510
00:25:16,420 --> 00:25:20,080
He's Yuan Song, a fellow officer
from the provincial department.

511
00:25:20,350 --> 00:25:20,870
What?

512
00:25:21,430 --> 00:25:23,260
Bold enough to kick open my door now,
aren't you?

513
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:23,770
Hey.

514
00:25:24,510 --> 00:25:25,030
Mister.

515
00:25:25,950 --> 00:25:27,960
I'll pay for the door if it's broken.

516
00:25:29,090 --> 00:25:31,090
Why did you have your people tail us?

517
00:25:32,490 --> 00:25:33,180
What now?

518
00:25:35,190 --> 00:25:36,250
You don't trust me?

519
00:25:36,470 --> 00:25:38,030
We don't trust anyone now.

520
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:43,450
Ye, come out.

521
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:48,570
Your mentor's here.

522
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:49,990
Do you trust him?

523
00:25:54,940 --> 00:25:55,870
What's going on?

524
00:25:56,660 --> 00:25:57,460
Mentor.

525
00:25:59,000 --> 00:25:59,660
You...

526
00:26:00,610 --> 00:26:03,870
Shouldn't you be recuperating
in the provincial capital?

527
00:26:04,370 --> 00:26:05,700
What are you doing here?

528
00:26:07,500 --> 00:26:09,260
Mai, give us a moment.

529
00:26:12,230 --> 00:26:13,360
I'll go have a smoke.

530
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:22,000
Mentor,

531
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:25,040
what's going on here?

532
00:26:28,090 --> 00:26:29,320
The cat's out of the bag.

533
00:26:29,320 --> 00:26:30,580
Might as well tell him.

534
00:26:33,710 --> 00:26:34,710
Here's the thing.

535
00:26:34,930 --> 00:26:36,320
After

536
00:26:36,570 --> 00:26:38,640
the Hangang Center accident,

537
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:39,580
someone

538
00:26:40,670 --> 00:26:42,590
tampered with my medical report

539
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:44,820
to make me retire early.

540
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:47,950
So I might as well take the way out.

541
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:52,530
Mentor...

542
00:26:54,030 --> 00:26:56,240
Do you have no trust in me at all?

543
00:26:57,020 --> 00:26:58,200
Why does this keep happening?

544
00:26:58,200 --> 00:26:58,730
Qin Feng,

545
00:26:59,270 --> 00:27:00,800
I specially arranged this.

546
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:04,480
The political landscape in Hanzhou
is highly complex,

547
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:06,740
with a tangled maze of interests behind.

548
00:27:07,430 --> 00:27:08,380
I invited your mentor

549
00:27:08,380 --> 00:27:10,190
to serve as an advisor
to the special task force

550
00:27:10,190 --> 00:27:12,050
so as to make use of his expertise.

551
00:27:13,410 --> 00:27:16,600
The provincial department
established this task force

552
00:27:16,760 --> 00:27:17,490
specifically

553
00:27:17,490 --> 00:27:19,150
for a covert investigation

554
00:27:19,620 --> 00:27:20,730
on Liu Yi's death

555
00:27:20,810 --> 00:27:22,300
and the truth

556
00:27:22,330 --> 00:27:24,390
behind the Hangang Center incident.

557
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:27,770
I just didn't expect you
to track us down here.

558
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:29,780
Ye,

559
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:31,700
your mentee is quite something,

560
00:27:31,700 --> 00:27:33,030
sharp as a tack.

561
00:27:35,710 --> 00:27:37,240
In light of that, I also have

562
00:27:37,930 --> 00:27:39,460
some information to offer.

563
00:27:40,420 --> 00:27:41,660
There was a fatality

564
00:27:42,130 --> 00:27:43,430
on the very day

565
00:27:44,150 --> 00:27:45,950
of the Hangang Center incident,

566
00:27:46,220 --> 00:27:47,370
but it was covered up.

567
00:27:47,370 --> 00:27:47,850
Yes.

568
00:27:48,430 --> 00:27:49,740
The task force already started

569
00:27:49,740 --> 00:27:50,740
investigating it

570
00:27:50,950 --> 00:27:52,280
in secret some time ago.

571
00:27:52,740 --> 00:27:53,600
We've gathered

572
00:27:53,700 --> 00:27:55,090
